    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "The sons of Japheth, Gomer,.... Here begins the genealogy of the sons of Noah after the flood; of the sons of Japheth the elder, in this and the two following verses; next of the sons of Ham, the younger brother, ",
